{"id":"ADR-009","file":".cleo/adrs/ADR-009-BRAIN-cognitive-architecture.md","title":"ADR-009: CLEO BRAIN Cognitive Architecture — Unified Reference","status":"accepted","date":"2026-02-22","accepted":"2026-02-22","relatedTasks":["T2996","T4797","T4911","T4912","T4913","T4914","T4915","T4916"],"summary":"Unifies the BRAIN cognitive architecture across scattered documents. Establishes SQLite as the runtime store for BRAIN memory (decisions, patterns, learnings), defines Vectorless RAG as the primary retrieval method, and maps the 5 BRAIN dimensions to CLEO's 9 canonical domains.","keywords":["brain","cognitive","memory","rag","vectorless","sqlite","retrieval","embeddings","dimensions"],"topics":["memory","storage","orchestrate","nexus"]}
